      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between everyday utility and meticulous care. The exterior retains a deep shine, though it shows minor, honest signs of road use consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean, with the upholstery and dashboard showing very little wear. Mechanically, it is in excellent working order; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and it has been serviced regularly at all recommended intervals. All electronics, including the infotainment and climate control systems, are fully functional. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any looming maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
