      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes both mechanical integrity and sophisticated presentation. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it offers a seamless blend of performance and long-term reliability. This offering represents an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that remains in commendable condition, ensuring a refined and confident driving experience for its next steward.",
      "price": 34500.0,
