    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. This car is in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your road trips and daily commutes! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
