    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 straight-six engine and a 6-speed manual transmission. This example boasts a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline with sharp throttle response facilitated by its individual throttle bodies. Critical mechanical updates have been addressed, including a VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis. The drivetrain is anchored by a functional M-Variable differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. While the finish shows light signs of use, the mechanical components\u2014including refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers\u2014remain tight and responsive. A technically sound specimen for the purist.",
